These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-1::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  bartender, pilot
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: house, trance
1. the pilot is somewhere to the left of the fan of house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Job           | pilot | bartender |
| Music-Genre   | trance     | house  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-2::.
2 different pets are kept: bird, ferret
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, trike
1. the person driving the bike is somewhere to the left of the owner of the bird##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |
| Pet         | ferret   | bird      |
| Transport   | bike | trike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: techno, reggae
The people use 2 different means of transport: snowmobile, trike
1. the fan of techno is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2    |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | techno    |
| Transport     | snowmobile | trike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-4::.
